        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1957-12-05T19:05:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1957-12-05T19:05:00-05:00" n="309"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d309">
                <head>309. Telegram From the <gloss type="from">Department of State</gloss> to the
                        <gloss type="to">Embassy in Indonesia</gloss>
                    <note n="1" type="source" xml:id="d309fn1">Source: Department of State, Central
                        Files, 756D.00/12–557. Top Secret; Priority. Drafted and approved by
                            <persName corresp="#p_CHSJ1">Cumming</persName> and cleared by <persName
                            corresp="#p_JHP1">Howard P. Jones</persName>.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1957-12-05T19:05:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 5, 1957—7:05 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>1226. For Ambassador only from <persName corresp="#p_CHSJ1">Cumming</persName>.
                    We have irrefutable evidence that despite official statements to contrary
                    responsible Indo authorities including highest military authority have ordered
                    subordinate commands throughout Republic to assist West Irian Liberation
                    Committee in taking over Dutch firms and facilities.</p>
                <p>Foregoing highly sensitive info is for your guidance only and should not be used
                    operationally in any way.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_DJF1">
                            <hi rend="strong">Dulles</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
